<m0>Intangibles: <m0>They're in the position they like best: underdogs with nothing to lose. If they steal a game in Philadelphia, they might be able to drain the Flyers in a steamy Miami Arena, where the Panthers have been super in the playoffs.<tl><tc><m0>Intangibles: <m0>The Flyboys aren't just happy to be here (--) they're thinking Cup. Also, even should they score an early rout, the lessons of Round 1 will prevent cockiness for the succeeding games.<tl><m2><ql>
